      <biogHist id="md5-013196da2c4a57733e0da9e7256fbd41">
        <p>Chemist, Administrator, 1924- .  Dr. Willard Allen joined the staff of the Department of  Chemistry in 1948.  He served as president of the Canadian Association of University Teachers,  1969-1970.  In 1971 he was appointed Associate Vice-President (Academic), to assist in the office's  responsibility for faculties, schools, research institutes and ancillary services, as well as the research  and Student Awards offices.  Dr. Allen retired in 1984.</p>
      </biogHist>
